data.description:
Come check out this fabulous, well-maintained two-story, 4 bedroom and 2.5 bathroom home located in the Columbia County Hidden Creek Community. Enter the open floor plan home through a welcoming foyer that leads you into the fittingly located living room and kitchen area. The eat-in kitchen boasts stainless steels appliances, beautiful stained cabinetry, nice sized pantry, granite countertops, and windows perfectly located to allow for natural lighting to flow in.  Pass through the charming living room with a decorative fireplace to reach the stairs that leads to all 4 bedrooms and the 2 full baths. The large owner's suite features a vaulted ceiling and an ensuite bathroom with dual vanity, walk-in closet, private toilet room and separate tub and shower.   The additional 3 bedrooms all have cathedral ceilings and are also spacious. Washer and dryer remains with the home. Fully landscaped yard with a sprinkler system in the front and backyard.  Several community amenities such as a community pool, clubhouse, playground, sidewalks, and streetlights. The home is conveniently located near I-20, restaurants, shopping centers, Patriots Park, the Columbia County fairground and is within close proximity of each of the zoned schools.  
If exact room measurements and schools are important, please reverify the provided information.
